Readable = concept rtypeof(T)
    proc read[T](r: Readable; x: var T)
    r.readFloat64 is float64
    r.readChar is char
    r.readInt8 is int8
    r.readUint8 is byte
    r.readInt32 is int32

    r.readStr(int) is string
    r.readUint32 is uint32
